features: 【Full Automatic Washer】 This portable washing machine is designed as a 2 in 1 compact washer. All you need to do is selecting the washing & spinning program and water level, then the mini laundry washer could work alone without your constant attention. This could save your time and you could do something more important.

【Multi-functional Control Panel】There’ re 10 washing programs, 4 water level mode and 8 water level selections on the control panel of the full automatic washing machine, which is convenient. LED display could clearly show the laundry time. And the child lock also ensure the normal operation of the washing machine while protecting the safety of your family.

【Solve Your Laundry Troubles】 Our compact washer is equipped with a drain pump, which could allow you to drain from different angles. With its powerful motor, you would have a convenient drainage operation.

【Portable and Space Saving】 This washing machine won’t take much space, thus making it an ideal choice for households with limit space, such as RV, Camping, Dorm and Apartments. You could easily store it. And you also don’t need to assemble this washer much before usage, hassle-free and easy to operate.

【Automatic Imbalance Adjustment】Other portable washer would be violent shaking and vibrating while washing or spinning. But our laundry washing machine would initiate its imbalance adjustment system to handle this kind of situation, thus ensure the safety and reduce noise.

【Large Capacity】The inner tub of this portable washer could load 17.7 lbs of clothes at one time, which is suitable for family of 3-4 members. The reference weight for all types of clothes would also be highlighted in the description and pictures.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: 2-in-1 Full Automatic Washing Machine - Release your hand! Our Krib Bling washing machine is full automatic controlled with 10 preset programs for soaking, washing, rinsing, dehydrating and stopping. This compact washer has 17.7 lbs large capacity to wash all clothes of the whole families. It is very suitable for your dormitory, apartment, RV, camping, garage, homestay, etc.

USAGE METHOD 1.Connect the water inlet pipe to the washing machine2.Check the connection between the inlet pipe and tap, turn on the tap3.Plug into the socket (don’t share the socket with other appliance)4.Put down the drain (our product is with a drain pump)5.Select the water level and program6.Start washing NOTE: 1.There is a period of time to start spin dry even if there is no water in the tub2.Clothing with colors may easily rub off and must be washed separately from other clothes3.The impeller will stop running if the water is below the minimum water level4.Do not use the water at a temperature more than 50°C5.All product are fully inspected and maybe some water stains or residual water will remain, please rest assured to use. All products are brand new
SPECIFICATION Load capacity 17.7 lbs Color Gold Dimensions 19.9*19.7*33.7 inch Voltage 110-120 V~，60 Hz Power 120 W (dehydrating)/200 W (washing)

Unlike other sellers, our washing machine is equipped with a drain pump for more efficient drainage. You can drain the dirty water from different angles. Note: We recommend that the height of drain pipe should not be more than 10 cm, or it may cause: drain not fluently, longer drain and stop working midway.

AUTO UNBALANCE DETECTION As the unbalance could be a very serious issue for washing machine. Our washer is able to automatically fix the unbalance issue through its Auto Unbalance Detection (AUD) function. It will also alert the user if the problem can't be fixed, ensuring a safe and pleasant experience. UPGRADED MOTOR The upgraded & professional motor are perfectly matched, with unique damping system and 4 leveling feet to greatly reduce the impact of tremor and noise. It will save the energy consumption comparing to similar models. HONEYCOMB DESIGNED TUB The honeycomb shaped inner tub can load 17.7 lbs at one time and wash many clothes for you. Diamond honeycomb design will not damage the clothing.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Arrived early and works perfectly.
reviews.reviewText: Good value. Arrived early and works perfectly. I couldn't be more pleased with the product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Washes great didn’t like the hose and changed it and it’s still leaking even after I switched it other then that works great. The hose to throw the water out is not plastic don’t like it is there a way to change that

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I appreciate the design and functions of the washer, but the drain problem discouraged us from keeping it. Normally a washer would drain at the end of the wash cycle, instead it is always leaking water so that water can’t build up so a wash can’t even happen. Whatever mechanism let’s the drain open at the end of the cycle is just stuck in the open position. No word from the seller/manufacturer after a few attempts. Unfortunately it’s gonna get shipped back.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very easy set up!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This is the best purchase I’ve made this year! It took all 15 minutes to set up. Once I figured out hire the rat guard fit at the bottom, then I set it on the dolly thing with wheel locks, hooked it up to the faucet and boom I was washing. Water will have water in it when you first get because they test it out and I appreciate it. Do not over load this and I believe it will last you a long while. I’ve got the protection plan too. I did a very small load of towels and selected the lowest water level possible and everything worked so well. Later on I did three loads within an hour and a half. As I was hanging the first load I started another one and the first load was nearly dry. The spin dryer feature is thee best and I’m line drying. I found an old phone cord and string it from wall to wall. Old school style. All of my clothes are dry and I’m folding them. My house smells amazing! It comes with the sink attachment and lucky for me everything fits. Tighten up the sink adapters and do not remove any of the “o” rings & you should be good to go. I love it! Thank you

reviews.reviewText: works great, holds more than I thought. fully automatic.

reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. No vibration felt on the floor, the noise is little, I only had to buy the water adapter , I just turn it on and don't worry about adjusting the water level, just select the # program and start and that's it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: All I see on this poor machine is defective equipment and false advertising. The wash cycle will not wash. The water stays there, the machine makes noise, a total disappointment and not recommended. Also, when it advertises it as a dryer - it's lying - it's a spinner and will still get your clothes wet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I got this so that I can wash my baby’s clothings separately from the adult clothings. Shipping speed was really fast and I finally got to set it up today and run it. It was easy setup and the machine is not very heavy. The size is bigger than I expected but it would still work for baby clothings even if I have a larger load. I test run it and it cleans just as efficient as a normal size washer machine. I would recommend it for anyone who needs a more portable washing machine or want to get one just for baby clothings like me.
